OL,7,FA British Airways flight attendant who
OL,8,Fwas found naked and high on drugs in a
OL,9,Fplane toilet during a transatlantic
OL,10,Fflight has been spared jail.
OL,12,FHaden Pentecost, 41, was handed a six-
OL,13,Fmonth prison sentence, suspended for a
OL,14,Fyear, after he admitted performing an
OL,15,Faviation function while under the
OL,16,Finfluence of drugs.
OL,18,FIsleworth Crown Court heard on Friday
OL,19,Fhow Pentecost was due to work on a
OL,20,Fflight from San Francisco to London
OL,21,FHeathrow in May.
