OL,7,FBefore the flight, he told colleagues
OL,8,Fhe had stomach cramps but insisted he
OL,9,Fwas fit for duty.
OL,11,FCabin managers later found him at the
OL,12,Fbottom of the stairs, looking
OL,13,Fdishevelled, pale, sweaty and behaving
OL,14,Ferratically.
OL,16,FHe then locked himself in a toilet
OL,17,Fand, when he emerged, was "completely
OL,18,Fnaked and oblivious" to the fact he
OL,19,Fhad no clothes on, prosecutor Natasha
OL,20,FLake told the court.
