OL,7,FA colleague struggled to make sense of
OL,8,Fwhat he was saying before dressing him
OL,9,Fand moving him into a free seat.
OL,11,FThe captain was alerted and, after
OL,12,Fspeaking with Pentecost, requested
OL,13,Fassistance from medical professionals
OL,14,Fon board.
OL,16,FHe was found to have dilated pupils,
OL,17,Fwas unable to answer what year it was
OL,18,For who the US president was, and drank
OL,19,F15 to 20 bottles of water during the
OL,20,Fflight, the court was told.
