OL,7,FHis behaviour caused a "huge
OL,8,Fdistraction" for the captain and crew,
OL,9,Fthough no passengers were aware of his
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FJon Harrison, defending Pentecost,
OL,13,Ftold the court that his client had
OL,14,Ftaken drugs in San Francisco to
OL,15,F"enhance a sexual experience" -
OL,16,Fsomething he admitted to doing before
OL,17,F- but questioned whether the strength
OL,18,Fof the substance was different this
OL,19,Ftime.
