OL,7,FThe flight landed at Heathrow, where
OL,8,Fparamedics met the aircraft and took
OL,9,FPentecost to Hillingdon Hospital.
OL,11,FA blood test later revealed Pentecost
OL,12,Fhad methamphetamine and amphetamine -
OL,13,Fa drug prescribed for ADHD and
OL,14,Fnarcolepsy - in his system. He was
OL,15,Flater dismissed from his job.
OL,17,FMs Lake said the offence carried a
OL,18,Fmaximum penalty of two years'
OL,19,Fimprisonment, but there were no
OL,20,Fsentencing guidelines to assist
OL,21,Fbecause the case was "quite unique".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
