OL,7,FShe told the court Pentecost had
OL,8,Ffailed to complete pre-flight safety
OL,9,Fchecks and that his colleagues had to
OL,10,Fmanage the 10-and-a-half-hour flight
OL,11,Fwithout his assistance.
OL,13,FHarrison said Pentecost had lost the
OL,14,Fcareer he "very much valued" and came
OL,15,Fbefore the court "a man without the
OL,16,Fprofession that he sought to develop
OL,17,Fafter Covid".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
