OL,7,FSentencing, Judge Hannah Duncan told
OL,8,Fhim: "You don't need me to tell you
OL,9,Fjust how serious this offence was.
OL,10,FCabin crew perform an essential safety
OL,11,Frole.
OL,13,F"They are there for the comfort of
OL,14,Fpassengers but if anything goes wrong
OL,15,Fit is up to you to make sure they are
OL,16,Fsafe.
