OL,7,F"It would have been frightening for
OL,8,Fany passengers to see you in that
OL,9,Fposition. You really let yourself
OL,10,Fdown. You are extremely ashamed, you
OL,11,Fare mortified, you are teetotal and
OL,12,Fyou will never take drugs again.
OL,14,F"You have comprehensively addressed
OL,15,Fthe behaviour that led to you being in
OL,16,Fthe dock today."
