OL,7,FThe judge noted there was a "great
OL,8,Fdeal of mitigation" in Pentecost's
OL,9,Fcase, including his previous good
OL,10,Fcharacter and immediate guilty plea,
OL,11,Fand that his behaviour had not been
OL,12,Faggressive or confrontational.
OL,14,FShe reduced his sentence from 12
OL,15,Fmonths to nine months due to
OL,16,Fmitigation, then to six months for his
OL,17,Fearly plea, before suspending it for
OL,18,F12 months.
